{"product_id":"bee-it-sun-spf30-50ml","title":"BEE IT SUN SPF30 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eSun cream which protects, nourishes and hydrates the skin, favouring an intense and even tan. Organic Aloe Vera extract, combined with sweet almond oil, zinc oxide, vitamin E, organic honey and propolis, helps prevent premature aging caused by exposure to UV rays. For hydrated, supple, soft and enviably tanned skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to face\/body before sun exposure, repeating the application frequently for a safe, even and long-lasting tan.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua [Water], Ethylhexyl methoxycinnamate, Octocrylene, Butyl methoxydibenzoylmethane, Glyceryl stearate SE, Cetearyl alcohol, Helianthus annuus (Sunflower) seed oil, Prunus amygdalus dulcis (Sweet almond) oil, Methylene bis-benzotriazolyl tetramethylbutylphenol, Phenoxyethanol, Parfum [Fragrance], Decyl glucoside, Citric acid, Glycerin, Titanium dioxide, Tocopheryl acetate, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Zinc oxide, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Propylene glycol, Xanthan gum, Mel\/Honey*, Propolis wax, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354659856711,"sku":null,"price":7.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-sun-spf30-50ml-603793.png?v=1739897345","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/bee-it-sun-spf30-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}